---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Cookie Policy" description="Learn about the cookies used on SimplifyCalculator and how to manage your consent." path="/cookie-policy">
  <div class="static-page">
    <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: July 17, 2026</em></p>
    <p>This site uses cookies to improve your experience and to analyze traffic. You can manage or withdraw your consent at any time using the cookie preferences banner that appears when you visit the site.</p>

    <p>Below is a summary of the categories of cookies used on SimplifyCalculator:</p>
    <ul class="lp-tips">
      <li><strong>Necessary:</strong> required for the site to function and to remember your cookie consent choices.</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> used by Google Analytics (via Google Tag Manager) to understand aggregate traffic patterns — which pages are visited and how often. These are only set after you consent.</li>
      <li><strong>Advertising:</strong> used by Google AdSense and its partners to serve and measure ads, including for personalized advertising where permitted. These are only set after you consent.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      You can opt out of personalized advertising at any time by visiting
      <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a>,
      or by adjusting your cookie preferences using the consent banner on this site.
    </p>
    <p>
      Questions about this policy? Contact us at
      <a href="mailto:contact@simplifycalculator.com">contact@simplifycalculator.com</a> or visit our
      <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
